Package: sacred
Type: Package
Title: Set of Sacred Texts Bible Data in Tidy Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("John", "Coene", , "jcoenep@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: John Coene <jcoenep@gmail.com>
Description: All 66 books comprising of the 'Apocrypha', the 'King James Bible', 
    the 'Greek New Testament', the 'Septuagint', the 'Tanach' and the 'Vulgate', as well
    as text mining utilities suited to Middle English.
